reviewtext: These are a good purchase if you break headphones as much as I do. What's the point of buying more expensive ones when they don't last much longer than the cheaper models? For the price I wasn't expecting much but I found them to be pretty comfortable and the volume is pretty good as well. Unlike the Koss headphones the Panasonic ones allow you to turn up the volume quite a bit and the overall sound quality was decent as well.
